(Version: 0.3)
2019-10-27  Masa Sakano
  * Added 3 executables textclean, head.rb, tail.rb in bin/ together with their tests
  * lib/plaintext.rb refactoring
    * Added a new constant `DEF_METHOD_OPTS`
  * bin/countchar refactoring

